22
00:02:13,769 --> 00:02:16,337
    No, I mean, look at me,
    I mean...

23
00:02:16,405 --> 00:02:18,673
   I'm not the criminal type.

24
00:02:18,741 --> 00:02:20,742
          Far from it.

25
