   <i>to do the right thing,</i>

29
00:02:33,489 --> 00:02:36,324
      <i>even with my garbage.</i>

30
00:02:36,392 --> 00:02:39,294
  <i>I volunteer my Sunday to help</i>
  <i>the visually impaired.</i>

31
00:02:39,361 --> 00:02:40,795
                 Is that a fact?

32
00:02:40,862 --> 00:02:43,665
             Kid, I got
