         <i>(horn sounds) </i>

52
00:03:40,356 --> 00:03:43,458
      <i>However, no matter</i>
      <i>how honorably we try</i>

53
00:03:43,525 --> 00:03:45,326
    <i>to conduct our own lives,</i>

