528
00:25:56,057 --> 00:25:58,258
        <i>Also your friend,</i>
        <i>Inga Mueller."</i>

529
00:25:59,526 --> 00:26:02,495
        I don't need
        your Nazi soup.

530
00:26:15,376 --> 00:26:17,244
 <i>(dog barking)</i>
 <i>(car door closes) </i>

531
00:26:17,312 --> 00:26:19,946
 <i>(Max) Schatzi,</i>
 <i>stay in the house.</i>

532
00:26:20,013 --> 00:26:22,315
 <i>(singing) </i>

533
00:26:22,382 --> 00:26:26,086
      <i>You know how they say</i>
      <i>you can't find love,</i>
      <i>it finds you?</i>

534
00:26:26,154 --> 00:26:28,221
       <i>Well, it's the same</i>
       <i>with hate.</i>

535
00:26:28,289 --> 00:26:30,090
      <i>It just takes someone</i>
