00:26:50,745 --> 00:26:52,145
       <i>(radio host)</i>
       <i>Hello, you're on the air.</i>

546
00:26:52,212 --> 00:26:54,147
 <i>(Jack)</i> I'd like to get back
 to that Luger case.

547
00:26:54,215 --> 00:26:56,482
       <i>I'm gonna need you</i>
