560
00:27:23,611 --> 00:27:25,545
          <i>(dial tone)</i>
      Hello?

561
00:27:29,417 --> 00:27:30,883
     Assholes!

562
00:27:30,951 --> 00:27:33,119
                <i>(Max)</i> My friend,
                my friend.

563
00:27:33,187 --> 00:27:35,322
     <i>(man)</i> Don't worry about
     a thing, all right?

564
00:27:36,390 --> 00:27:37,990
       <i>(man #2)</i> Good night, Max.

565
00:27:41,629 --> 00:27:43,897
      <i>I sensed I was headed</i>
      <i>for trouble</i>

566
00:27:43,965 --> 00:27:47,700
   <i>when I began spending hours</i>
   <i>in my attic watching Luger,</i>

567
00:27:47,768 --> 00:27:49,636
        <i>in the morning</i>
        <i>at his apple tree</i>

568
00:27:49,703 --> 00:27:52,639
    <i>and at night during</i>
    <i>those damned fundraisers.</i>

569
00:27:52,706 --> 00:27:56,009
    <i>My God, I'd been obsessed</i>
    <i>with women before,</i>

570
00:27:56,077 --> 00:27:59,512
      <i>but never with a man.</i>

571
00:27:59,579 --> 00:28:00,947
And I walk over to her,
and I'm trying to relax her

572
00:28:01,015 --> 00:28:02,682
and calm her down
and I said, "I like your hair."

