00:29:03,910 --> 00:29:07,980
that I feel
I don't have to be there.

597
00:29:08,048 --> 00:29:09,515
              It's a good thing?

598
00:29:09,583 --> 00:29:11,651
Yeah, it's the freedom
to be alone

