00:50:00,733 --> 00:50:03,068
        <i>Unh-unh. No way.</i>

933
00:50:03,135 --> 00:50:05,370
      <i>He wasn't good enough</i>
      <i>for suicide.</i>

934
00:50:06,806 --> 00:50:08,740
   <i>I had to let the world know</i>

935
00:50:08,808 --> 00:50:10,742
      <i>that he was punished</i>
      <i>for his crime...</i>

936
00:50:10,810 --> 00:50:12,744
   <i>without taking any credit,</i>
   <i>of course.</i>

937
00:50:12,812 --> 00:50:14,980
    <i>I mean, getting caught</i>
    <i>was not part of my plan.</i>

938
00:50:15,047 --> 00:50:16,982
      <i>So to set the record</i>
      <i>straight,</i>

939
00:50:17,049 --> 00:50:19,217
   <i>I knocked off a quick note</i>
   <i>to the police.</i>

940
00:50:20,787 --> 00:50:22,988
      <i>(man)</i> "Luger did not
      take his own life.

