      This crime scene's a mess.

956
00:51:04,898 --> 00:51:07,265
          Look at all these
          footprints and debris.

957
00:51:07,333 --> 00:51:10,035
           What the hell's this?

958
00:51:10,102 --> 00:51:12,070
That's sauerkraut.

