00:51:21,414 --> 00:51:22,881
   We got a literate letter,

964
00:51:22,949 --> 00:51:24,883
    we got a revenge killing
    by poison

965
00:51:24,951 --> 00:51:27,419
         with the most
         likely suspect
         a party guest.

966
00:51:27,486 --> 00:51:30,422
Sounds like a case
for "Hercules Parrot."

