00:51:35,294 --> 00:51:37,295
              <i>"is a greater evil</i>
              <i>than his murder,</i>

970
00:51:37,363 --> 00:51:40,164
    <i>"so killing Luger</i>
    <i>became the moral imperative.</i>

971
00:51:40,233 --> 00:51:43,568
       <i>Sincerely..."</i>
       <i>Obviously, it's unsigned.</i>

