00:54:17,790 --> 00:54:20,625
          and two-speed function
          record and playback.

1030
00:54:20,693 --> 00:54:22,193
      It's also voice-activated,

1031
00:54:22,261 --> 00:54:24,095
          comes with
          a separate microphone,

1032
00:54:24,163 --> 00:54:27,098
   and check this out--
