00:55:38,203 --> 00:55:40,238
      <i>a bizarre case</i>
      <i>of mistaken identity.</i>

1061
00:55:40,305 --> 00:55:42,473
      <i>The man murdered </i>
      <i>for being Karl Luger,</i>

1062
00:55:42,541 --> 00:55:43,875
      <i>The Beast of Berkau,</i>

