00:55:43,943 --> 00:55:45,777
      <i>has now been</i>
      <i>positively identified</i>

1064
00:55:45,845 --> 00:55:47,612
    <i>as Corporal Max Mueller,</i>

1065
00:55:47,680 --> 00:55:49,614
       <i>a lowly cook</i>
       <i>in the German army.</i>

1066
00:55:49,682 --> 00:55:53,118
     <i>Mueller's wartime file</i>
     <i>was among documents...</i>
                      No.

